
  Marshtomp    Water Type Pokémon

  The surface of MARSHTOMP’s body 
  is enveloped by a thin, sticky 
  film that enables it to live 
  on land.  Marshtomp plays 
  in mud on beaches when the ocean 
  tide is low. 
	   Evolution Chain
  Mudkip ► Marshtomp ► Swampert

